  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Seven factors are fully assessed with achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels; six factors are marked not-applicable with documented rationale. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. Decision: Accepted.",
